title: As a user, I want to view order history
description: As a user, I want to access a detailed history of my past orders to track my purchase records.

title: As an administrator, I want to implement session management
description: As an administrator, I want to manage user sessions to maintain security and prevent unauthorized access.

title: As a user, I want to filter products by price range
description: As a user, I want to set a price range to filter products and find items within my budget.

title: As a user, I want to receive push notifications for order updates
description: As a user, I want to receive push notifications on my mobile device for updates on order status and delivery.

title: As an administrator, I want to enable user feedback
description: As an administrator, I want to implement a user feedback system to gather insights for system improvements.

title: As a user, I want to access customer support
description: As a user, I want to have easy access to customer support for assistance with inquiries and issues.

title: As an administrator, I want to enable social media sharing
description: As an administrator, I want to add social media sharing options to allow users to share products and content.

title: As a user, I want to view product availability at nearby stores
description: As a user, I want to check product availability at nearby physical stores for in-store purchases.

title: As a user, I want to add products to my favorites
description: As a user, I want to add products to my favorites list for quick access and future reference.

title: As an administrator, I want to implement data encryption
description: As an administrator, I want to encrypt sensitive data to ensure secure transmission and storage.

title: As a user, I want to view product images from different angles
description: As a user, I want to see multiple images of a product from different angles to get a better view before purchase.

title: As an administrator, I want to enable guest checkout
description: As an administrator, I want to allow guest checkout for users who prefer not to create an account.

title: As a user, I want to see product recommendations
description: As a user, I want to receive personalized product recommendations based on my browsing and purchase history.

title: As an administrator, I want to implement user activity logs
description: As an administrator, I want to maintain activity logs for users to monitor system usage and detect anomalies.

title: As a user, I want to track order delivery on a map
description: As a user, I want to track my order's delivery progress on a map in real-time for accurate tracking.

title: As a user, I want to receive product recommendations via email
description: As a user, I want to receive personalized product recommendations through email for convenient access.

title: As an administrator, I want to implement user reviews moderation
description: As an administrator, I want to review and moderate user-submitted product reviews to ensure appropriateness and authenticity.

title: As a user, I want to see recently viewed products
description: As a user, I want to view a list of recently viewed products for quick access to previous selections.

title: As an administrator, I want to enable multi-language support
description: As an administrator, I want to provide multi-language support for users in different regions and languages.

title: As a user, I want to save my cart for later
description: As a user, I want to save the contents of my shopping cart to revisit and complete the purchase later.
